column2: Jim Peterson and neighbor Jerry Woods did the test for the first time on Lake Montanis. Clear day in the middle 70's.  As far as we know there is not a depth of 14 ' but 10' plus.  The lake is in need of testing with the algae blueish-green and many more weeds in the last 3 years around my property on the north side of the lake as well as others.
Blue sky about 80 degrees Blue sky about 80 degrees
In the past week we received 4 inches of rain
